49:27.897 --> 49:29.295
Some kind of wolves.

49:33.603 --> 49:37.637
Keep running.
I'll make mincemeat out of 'em.

49:37.639 --> 49:39.676
That's right, come on.

49:44.913 --> 49:46.746
Open the door!

49:46.748 --> 49:49.218
Let us in! Let us in!

49:52.587 --> 49:54.889
- Did you see that?
- What are those things?

49:54.891 --> 49:57.427
- Monsters!
- Hurry, get inside!

49:59.494 --> 50:01.829
Hunter, no, stay!

50:01.831 --> 50:03.831
Why aren't they attacking?

50:03.833 --> 50:07.634
It's like they're
waiting for something.

50:07.636 --> 50:09.603
Look at that cloud.

50:09.605 --> 50:11.704
It's weird,
like something's inside it.

50:11.706 --> 50:14.643
