50:37.799 --> 50:39.532
No, it can't be true.

50:39.534 --> 50:40.668
Oh, no.

50:40.670 --> 50:42.603
What are you doing?

50:42.605 --> 50:43.673
I'm saving you.

50:56.786 --> 50:59.755
Get inside!

51:00.989 --> 51:02.192
Leif!

51:03.525 --> 51:05.361
It's the ice dragon!

51:07.563 --> 51:09.900
