in dragons?

56:31.052 --> 56:33.152
No, no, I'm coming around.

56:35.690 --> 56:37.257
Okay, okay!

56:37.259 --> 56:39.659
Foolish boy.

56:39.661 --> 56:44.565
Your kind has given me the power
to rule this world!

56:44.567 --> 56:45.799
What do you mean?

56:45.801 --> 56:48.569
With the old man dead,

56:48.571 --> 56:51.938
my powers will soon be
unstoppable!

56:51.940 --> 56:54.340
Nicholai is dead?

56:54.342 --> 56:57.744
Yes, and with him
the cursed song as well.

56:57.746 --> 56:59.346
No, he can't be!

57:03.252 --> 57:05.652
Hungry, my pets?

57:05.654 --> 57:07.223
Then take him!

