57:16.230 --> 57:22.268
♪ For the sea and the sky
that was made ♪

57:22.270 --> 57:23.337
♪ We sing praise ♪

57:23.339 --> 57:25.371
Melody?

57:25.373 --> 57:28.741
♪ For the light
that brings hope ♪

