♪ And the promise
that love guides our way ♪

57:34.984 --> 57:38.652
♪ We give thanks ♪

57:38.654 --> 57:41.154
♪ We sing praise ♪

57:41.156 --> 57:43.293
♪ On this day ♪

57:47.929 --> 57:49.965
Melody, go back!

57:55.404 --> 57:56.639
Melody!

58:10.052 --> 58:11.918
No!

58:27.835 --> 58:30.237
Huh? Why aren't we dead?

58:30.239 --> 58:33.105
It's the song.
It's protecting us.

58:33.107 --> 58:35.877
The ice dragon
can't hurt us anymore.

58:37.946 --> 58:39.949
Come on, people!

58:42.750 --> 58:45.052
♪ There's no evil or darkness ♪

58:45.054 --> 58:46.753
♪ Can stand in our way ♪

58:46.755 --> 58:50.023
♪ With the faith
and the courage to believe ♪

58:50.025 --> 58:53.427
♪ That the song has the power
to change everything ♪

58:53.429 --> 58:57.297
♪ Come what may
we will say ♪

58:57.299 --> 59:00.933
♪ We give thanks ♪

59:00.935 --> 59:04.137
♪ We sing praise ♪

59:04.139 --> 59:08.945
♪ On this day ♪

59:21.223 --> 59:23.255
Hunter!

59:23.257 --> 59:24.393
Hunter, no!

59:36.739 --> 59:38.141
No!

59:40.775 --> 59:42.110
Nicholai?

59:43.112 --> 59:47.183
Back to your cave, Dracon!

59:56.257 --> 59:57.960
The Guardians of Light!

